OL,3,CTrump raises doubts about election
OL,4,Cinterference ahead of US midterms
OL,6,FDonald Trump has again raised doubts
OL,7,Fabout the legitimacy of US elections,
OL,8,Fas the country heads towards mid-terms
OL,9,Fin November.
OL,11,FThe US president used a primetime
OL,12,Faddress on Thursday night to dispute
OL,13,Fhis loss in 2020 and to appeal for
OL,14,Fmore restrictive voting laws, despite
OL,15,Fhis theories about election
OL,16,Finterference having been debunked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
