OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784357293
OL,3,CTrump raises doubts about election
OL,4,Cinterference ahead of US midterms
OL,6,F"America is back and doing really
OL,7,Fwell, but we still have a major
OL,8,Fchallenge that must be urgently
OL,9,Faddressed, because no country can be
OL,10,Fgreat without fair and honest
OL,11,Felections," he said.
OL,13,FHe went as far as to say that US
OL,14,Felections were "worse than any Third
OL,15,FWorld country".
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
