OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784357293
OL,3,CTrump raises doubts about election
OL,4,Cinterference ahead of US midterms
OL,6,FCritics have accused Trump of trying
OL,7,Fto sow confusion and spread
OL,8,Fmisinformation ahead of the mid-terms,
OL,9,Fwhich could see Republicans lose
OL,10,Fcontrol of one or both houses of
OL,11,FCongress.
OL,13,FA previous intelligence assessment
OL,14,Ffound no evidence that foreign
OL,15,Finterference had impacted the outcome
OL,16,Fof the 2020 presidential race, which
OL,17,Fhe lost to Joe Biden.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
