PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784357293
OL,3,CTrump raises doubts about election
OL,4,Cinterference ahead of US midterms
OL,6,FTrump has long claimed the election
OL,7,Fwas stolen from him, despite dozens of
OL,8,Fcourt cases finding no proof of
OL,9,Fwidespread fraud. He did not raise
OL,10,Fdoubts about his election wins in 2016
OL,11,For 2024.
OL,13,FMajor television networks ABC and NBC,
OL,14,Falong with CNN, opted not broadcast
OL,15,FTrump's address on their main
OL,16,Fchannels, leading the president to
OL,17,Fclaim they were involved in a "plot"
OL,18,Fand should lose their licences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
