OL,3,CTrump raises doubts about election
OL,4,Cinterference ahead of US midterms
OL,6,FTrump focused on Chinese interference
OL,7,Fin parts of his speech, but avoided
OL,8,Fcriticising Chinese President Xi
OL,9,FJinping directly, and did not mention
OL,10,FRussia at all in reference to the
OL,11,Felections, despite intelligence
OL,12,Fofficials having said the country
OL,13,Fengaged in wide-ranging influence
OL,14,Fcampaigns intended to boost Trump's
OL,15,Fresults in 2016 and 2020.
OL,17,FTrump's focus on interference in the
OL,18,Frun-up to the midterms suggests how he
OL,19,Fcould try to undermine results later
OL,20,Fin the year if he does not like the
OL,21,Fresult.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
