OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784357293
OL,3,CTrump raises doubts about election
OL,4,Cinterference ahead of US midterms
OL,6,FWhile the president revealed a series
OL,7,Fof newly declassified documents
OL,8,Frelating to the 2020 election,
OL,9,Fanalysis by ITV News' US partner CNN
OL,10,Ffound that they largely covered
OL,11,Fpreviously known potential
OL,12,Fvulnerabilities in the system,
OL,13,Fincluding in relation to Chinese
OL,14,Finterference, and did not provide any
OL,15,Fevidence to show that votes had been
OL,16,Fmanipulated or that the 2020 election
OL,17,Fhad been altered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
