PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784357293
OL,3,CTrump raises doubts about election
OL,4,Cinterference ahead of US midterms
OL,6,FAfter the speech all 24 Democratic
OL,7,Fgovernors put out a statement alleging
OL,8,FTrump intended to "intimidate and
OL,9,Fsilence voters".
OL,11,F"It's deeply alarming that President
OL,12,FTrump continues to try to undermine
OL,13,Ffree and fair elections," the
OL,14,FDemocratic governors said. "No amount
OL,15,Fof lies and conspiracy theories can
OL,16,Fchange the fact that our country's
OL,17,Felections have repeatedly been proven
OL,18,Fto be safe and secure."
